FBIS4-21869 "jptot015__l94034" JPRS-TOT-94-015-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 6 April 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA REGIONAL AFFAIRS Hijacker Explains Reasons for Seeking Asylum Hijacker Explains Reasons for Seeking Asylum NC0604131594 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1250 GMT 6 Apr 94 NC0604131594 Cairo MENA Arabic BFN [Excerpt] Luxor, 6 Apr (MENA)--Mahjub Husayn Muhammad, the hijacker of the Sudanese airliner, has stated that he chose to seek political asylum in Egypt because it is a safe and dear country. He said that the political, economic, and social situation in Sudan is deteriorating. [passage omitted]
